data.description: 38265 Crocus is a gorgeous condo in the heart of Palm Desert at the Palm Valley Country Club. Wonderful completely remodeled home offers 1,598 of living space with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This astonishing open concept floorplan delivers an amazing kitchen with white quartz counter tops, stunning back splash and stainless-steel appliances, bathrooms consist of custom tile work and marble counter tops. The incredible patio views of the fairways and water feature will certainly leave you in aww. Come and enjoy PVCC which offers two 18-hole golf courses, 40 community pools/spas, 16 Tennis courts, pickle ball, fitness center and an amazing clubhouse.  Don't miss the opportunity to live the lifestyle you have always wanted. Call today for a private showing.
